quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,64,"Amman yabdao alkhalqa thumma yuAAeeduhuwaman yarzuqukum mina assama-i wal-ardia-ilahun maAAa Allahi qul hatoo burhanakumin kuntum sadiqeen"
  27,65,"Qul la yaAAlamu man fee assamawatiwal-ardi alghayba illa Allahu wamayashAAuroona ayyana yubAAathoon"
  27,66,"Bali iddaraka AAilmuhum fee al-akhiratibal hum fee shakkin minha bal hum minha AAamoon"
  27,67,"Waqala allatheena kafaroo a-ithakunna turaban waabaona a-innalamukhrajoon"
  27,68,"Laqad wuAAidna hatha nahnuwaabaona min qablu in hatha illaasateeru al-awwaleen"
  27,69,"Qul seeroo fee al-ardi fanthurookayfa kana AAaqibatu almujrimeen"
  27,70,"Wala tahzan AAalayhim walatakun fee dayqin mimma yamkuroon"
  27,71,"Wayaqooloona mata hathaalwaAAdu in kuntum sadiqeen"
  27,72,"Qul AAasa an yakoona radifa lakumbaAAdu allathee tastaAAjiloon"
  27,73,"Wa-inna rabbaka lathoo fadlinAAala annasi walakinna aktharahum layashkuroon"
  27,74,"Wa-inna rabbaka layaAAlamu ma tukinnusudooruhum wama yuAAlinoon"
  27,75,"Wama min gha-ibatin fee assama-iwal-ardi illa fee kitabin mubeen"
  27,76,"Inna hatha alqur-ana yaqussuAAala banee isra-eela akthara allathee humfeehi yakhtalifoon"
